    "description": "利用 Stellaris 至今最身历其境的内容包《Aquatics Species Pack》，在广阔的银河系中航行，拥抱航海文明的生活！让一波全新的帝国可自定义选项加入您的 Stellaris，包含全新物种肖像、船舰套组、起源以及更多内容。<br><br>穿上潜水蛙鞋、背上氧气筒，深入探索《Aquatics Species Pack》的海洋世界：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新起源：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/4cef84476794190d95dd68fd00bac7de.poster.avif?t=1716896973\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/4cef84476794190d95dd68fd00bac7de.webm?t=1716896973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/4cef84476794190d95dd68fd00bac7de.mp4?t=1716896973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>与龙共舞！：</strong>这只古老的神秘野兽在您的家园徘徊，它的深蓝色鳞片环绕着您那卑微的王国。您与这只高傲生物的关系将会决定它愿意为保护您或摧毁您所付出的心力... 最好不要惹它不开心。<br><br></li><li><strong>海洋天堂：</strong>这些和平的文明在丰饶的环境中，过着平和的生活。没有天敌、食物储备和加成，享受不受阻碍的成长和富裕。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/05ab12c293e08974f7cfcd3a8b1b5119.poster.avif?t=1716896973\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/05ab12c293e08974f7cfcd3a8b1b5119.webm?t=1716896973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/05ab12c293e08974f7cfcd3a8b1b5119.mp4?t=1716896973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新特性</h2>水生：当物种进化到能在海洋世界中繁衍生息时，它们也是其他生物眼中典型的“离开水的鱼”。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新文明 </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[*[b]]垂钓者 (海洋的恩赐)：[/b]新鲜的海鲜和稀有的珍珠是航海员生活的一部分好处。前往渔业地区，利用这些有价值的消费品挣钱。</ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新超凡飞升</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>水中心：</strong>曾经在水下携带过重物吗？更轻松了，对吧？当您大部分时间都在水下时，就会找出更便宜、更快速的方法来改变周围的环境。将星球地球化变成海洋世界，或收集其他星球的水来壮大自己。打造太空中的沙堡！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装饰物件</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/a2e2705a3a9f93395184021291a57576.poster.avif?t=1716896973\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/a2e2705a3a9f93395184021291a57576.webm?t=1716896973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749080/extras/a2e2705a3a9f93395184021291a57576.mp4?t=1716896973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>全新船舰套组有利落优雅的外型，专为协助您在太空中快速穿梭而设计。<br></li><li>全新水生龙：一条全新雄伟的太空龙将让星空熠熠生辉。<br></li><li>全新顾问：受公海冒险小说启发的航海顾问，带着他的建议一同在星空航行。<br></li><li>15 幅全新水生肖像以协助您拥抱全新的存在 </li></ul><br><strong>有些功能可能需要单独贩售的内容</strong>",
